headline: Three Big Reasons to Love Howmet (HWM)
summary: Howmet currently trades at $114.80 and has been a dream stock for shareholders. It’s returned 268% since December 2019, nearly tripling the S&P 500’s 91.9% gain. The company has also beaten the index over the past six months as its stock price is up 38% thanks to its solid quarterly results.
